{"article_id":"tYFugQE94tgjusrB","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"China reported its highest daily coronavirus death toll Tuesday , the 103 additional fatalities","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"pushing the total past 1,100","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"and providing a somber warning","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"that the epidemic represents `` a very grave threat to the rest of the world . ''","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"All but two of the 1,115 deaths","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"attributed to the outbreak","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"that emerged in December","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"have been in mainland China .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"The virus is continuing to spread into other countries :","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"Almost 500 of the 45,182 confirmed cases are outside China .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"The Centers for Disease Control and Prevention this week reported the 13th case in the U.S .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"`` The rise in mortality cases is concerning , ''","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"Ogbonnaya Omenka , an assistant professor and public health specialist at Butler University 's College of Pharmacy and Health Sciences , told .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"`` In China , health workers are overstretched ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"and diagnostic processes are not keeping up with the cases . ''","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"Omenka said","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"testing and confirming cases takes longer","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"because of a shortage of diagnostic tools .","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"And supportive treatment is not available for many cases","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"because of the shortage of facilities and health workers ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"For the latest on coronavirus :","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"Get 's Daily Briefing in your inbox","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"A team from the World Health Organization arrived in China this week","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"to lay the groundwork for a larger international team","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"that will aid the Chinese effort","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"while learning traits of the outbreak","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"that could help scientists contain its spread ,","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"WHO Director-General Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus said .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"`` With 99 % of cases in China , this remains very much an emergency for that country , but one","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"that holds a very grave threat for the rest of the world , ''","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"Tedros said .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"`` It ' s hard to believe","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"that just two months ago , this virus","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"- which has come to captivate the attention of media , financial markets and political leaders -","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"was completely unknown to us . ''","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"In the U.S. , almost 200 people","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"evacuated from Wuhan , China , on the first charter flight from the country","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"were being released Tuesday ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"said Anne Schuchat , principal deputy director of the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"She said","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"the 195 people had been monitored for symptoms of the respiratory virus for the past 14 days , the maximum incubation time .","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"None had common symptoms such as fever or coughing .","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"Of the 800 people","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"evacuated on five separate charter flights ,","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"only one person has been confirmed with coronavirus ,","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"Schuchat said .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"Schuchat said","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"coronavirus seems to spread more easily than SARS","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"- severe acute respiratory syndrome -","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"but appears to be less lethal .","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"SARS ,","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"which originated in China","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"and spread globally in 2003 ,","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"killed about one in 10 people .","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"So far , the death rate for coronavirus is about 2 % in China ,","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"and that figure might drop","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"as China counts people with milder cases .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"The transmissibility of the virus may be more similar to that of the flu or the common cold ,","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"she said .","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"`` It may be with additional cases ,","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"particularly if they don ' t involve symptoms or very mild symptoms ,","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"that it will be very difficult to block the spread , ''","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"Schuchat said .","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"US workers at Hong Kong consulate given OK","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"to leave","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"The State Department has authorized the voluntary departure of non-emergency employees at the U.S. Consulate General in Hong Kong .","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"One death and 49 coronavirus cases have been reported in the administrative region of China .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"The decision","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"to allow employees and their families the option","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"of leaving","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"was made `` out of an abundance of caution , ''","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"a department spokesperson said in a statement .","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"The status will be reviewed in 30 days ,","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"the statement said .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"Coronavirus , explained :","depth":4},{"id":76,"text":"Everything","depth":5},{"id":77,"text":"you need to know about the deadly virus","depth":5},{"id":78,"text":"WHO announced a formal name for the coronavirus","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"- COVID-19 .","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"Tedros said","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"officials needed a name","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"that did not refer to a geographical location , an animal , an individual or group of people .","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"It also had to be pronounceable and related to the disease ,","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"`` Having a name matters ,","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"to prevent the use of other names","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"that can be inaccurate or stigmatizing , ''","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"`` It also gives us a standard format","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"to use for any future coronavirus outbreaks . ''","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"The new coronavirus could become a pandemic :","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"What is that ?","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"Should I be worried ?","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"The CDC confirmed the 13th U.S. coronavirus case Monday .","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"The case ,","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"detected in California ,","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"involved a patient under a federal quarantine order at Marine Corps Air Station Miramar near San Diego","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"after recently returning from Wuhan .","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"Wuhan and Hubei province are where the outbreak of respiratory illness","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"caused by the virus","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"was discovered in December .","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"The CDC said","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"it was conducting a thorough `` contact investigation '' of the person","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"who has tested positive","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"to determine","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"whether friends , relatives or others are should be considered high-risk .","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"WHO ,","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"which declared a global emergency two weeks ago ,","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"on Tuesday convened a two-day global forum","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"to encourage international action","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"and fast-track new tests , treatments and vaccines .","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"The forum ,","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"meeting in Geneva","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"with some experts attending remotely ,","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"includes scientists , researchers from public health agencies , regulatory experts and bioethicists with expertise in research emergencies .","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"`` We want you to know","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"that we stand with you in solidarity","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"and we wish you courage , patience , success and good health in these extremely trying circumstances , ''","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"Tedros told participants .","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"Chinese doctor dies :","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"He had been censured for warning about coronavirus","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"In Japan , the government is considering a plan","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"to release some elderly passengers with chronic illnesses from a cruise ship","depth":15},{"id":124,"text":"quarantined in Yokohama","depth":15},{"id":125,"text":"over coronavirus infection fears ,","depth":14},{"id":126,"text":"multiple media outlets in Japan reported .","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"One hundred seventy-four of the 3,700 people aboard have tested positive for the virus .","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"The government had asked about 3,600 passengers and crew members to stay on board during the two-week isolation period through Feb. 19 .","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"About 80 % of the 2,666 passengers are 60 or older ;","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"215 are in their 80s","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"and 11 are in their 90s ,","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"authorities say .","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"Masahiro Kami , head of the nonprofit Medical Governance Research Institute , told Kyodo News","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"that elderly people with chronic illnesses","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"that stress from confinement to cramped cabins","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"could make them `` susceptible to virus infection","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"and risk their lives . ''","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"Outbreak :","depth":2},{"id":139,"text":"A look inside the cruise ship","depth":3},{"id":140,"text":"quarantined by the coronavirus","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":281,"left":278,"right":280,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":278,"left":215,"right":277,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":215,"left":161,"right":214,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":161,"left":148,"right":160,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":148,"left":144,"right":147,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":142,"right":143,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":142,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":146,"right":7,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":146,"left":4,"right":145,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":150,"right":159,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":149,"right":10,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":149,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":151,"right":158,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":152,"right":157,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":157,"left":154,"right":156,"relation":"joint","nucleari